45
00:03:57,560 --> 00:04:02,299
colleague in the RAF also wrote on Bader’s
behalf and got a slightly more positive answer,

46
00:04:02,299 --> 00:04:07,870
“No” but if war was to break out they’d
almost certainly want his services if the

47
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:11,269
doctor agreed.
