51
00:04:26,860 --> 00:04:31,080
Whilst training he got to fly the Hurricane
fighter aircraft and his final report described

52
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:37,939
his flying ability as “exceptional”. He
was posted to 19 squadron in Duxford. In his

53
00:04:37,939 --> 00:04:43,170
new squadron he got to fly the Spitfire for
the first time. Soon he became leader of his

54
00:04:43,170 --> 00:04:48,569
section and eventually became a flight lieutenant
