105
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:13,688
Once in Germany they had given him his legs
back, but the living conditions were dire.

106
00:09:13,688 --> 00:09:19,679
Here Bader was part of several plans to escape,
including digging tunnels and picking locks,

107
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:24,859
but none of them were successful for him.
The most extravagant plan came later at another

108
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:29,329
camp, when he was involved in making a glider
